Hey there! It’s Lennart Pagel and I will take you with me on an amazing road trip across Germany, Denmark, Sweden and for the most part Norway. The picture shows what basically was home to me and some friends on our over 7.000 kilometer long journey. For this crazy amount of driving hours the G was a real blessing. While taking us to the most beautiful, remote places, it at the same time offered so much on-the-road-comfort. ?? @lennart 
@theolator @nils_loewe @jannispagel [Mercedes-Benz G500 | Fuel consumption combined: 12.3 l/100 km |CO2 emissions combined: 289 g/km]

#MBPhotoPass #MercedesBenz #Mercedes #Benz # Gclass #G500 #lifestyle #roadtrip #4x4 #Norway #Denmark #Sweden #Germany

After miles and miles of driving, we had to stop for the night. Back on mainland and so far up North we were rewarded with the best camp out experience we could ever imagine. Simply a fantastic experience, even if the polar lights made us stay up late. Unfortunately the amazing experience came to an end at our most Northern stop. It was an amazing experience. Thanks for jumping the backseat with me.

